vetica, sans-serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 11px;\\\">Sa&uacute;de em primeiro lugar: consultoria dermatol&oacute;gica especializada em sa&uacute;de da pele.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1;\\\" align=\\\"center\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #808080;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 11px;\\\">Responsabilidade: testes rigorosos de qualidade no desenvolvimento de cada produto.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1;\\\" align=\\\"center\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #808080;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 11px;\\\">Foco no cliente: capacita&ccedil;&atilde;o e desenvolvimento de produtos para todos os tipos de pele.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p>\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1;\\\" align=\\\"center\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<p style=\\\"font-family: arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1;\\\" align=\\\"center\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #808080;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size: 11px;\\\">PELE SAUD&Aacute;VEL<br \\/> O Brasil &eacute; um pa&iacute;s com grande incid&ecirc;ncia solar, o que aumenta o risco de c&acirc;ncer da pele. N&atilde;o por acaso, esse &eacute; o tipo de c&acirc;ncer mais comum no nosso pa&iacute;s. Por isso, a <span class=\\\"m_2892233598164390206m_-2063397051310651727m_-4275010779751737721m_394069070049657089m_-196584876623295506m_939931076366045025m_-7207494676733482353m_5985328848932110003m_2081301634921109004m_-657900294670147593m_-5094882047373223182m_6038020382194209637m_-1506821621542000624m_4867260655026985700m_-3697883245682610051m_5860268020959797336m_2325921981902193481m_-114481467839063642m_-6660464756882400210m_-3938936221861401506m_-7745476871295997380m_-6605852422651448954m_5799638064240227518m_4717389910573412766m